content.rendered:
Directed by Sudheer Varma.

Written by Arjun. Carthyk. Carthyk-Arjun. Sudheer Varma.

Cast Nikhil Siddharth(Sri Keshav Sharma ‘Keshava’). Ritu Varma(Sathyabhama). Isha Koppikar(Sharmila Mishra) . Ajay(Nakul). Brahmaji(Bheemeshwar). Jeeva(Police Commissioner). Vennela Kishore(Ranga). Madhunandan(Ranga’s friend). Ravi Prakash(CI Ravi). Priyadarshi Pulikonda(Keshava’s friend (as Priyadarshi)). Rao Ramesh(Krishna Murthy).Raja Ravindra. Sameer(Keshava’s father). Satya(Taxi Driver Malinga).Sudharshan

Language Telugu.

Producers Vivek Kuchibhotla. Abhishek Nama.

Production Abhishek Pictures.
